msgid_plural "Stalkers"
msgstr[0] ""
msgstr[1] ""

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'Stalker'}
#: .\Monsters\closeBandits.json
msgid ""
"Festooned with gear, these stalkers have entered the New England Exclusion "
"zone seeking their own treasure, or perhaps they just want the thrill of "
"adventure."
msgstr ""

#: .\Monsters\closeBandits.json
msgid "Tazer Bandit"
msgid_plural "Tazer Bandits"
msgstr[0] ""
msgstr[1] ""

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'Tazer Bandit'}
#: .\Monsters\closeBandits.json
msgid ""
"This bandit is particularly unique, as they have a tazer to shock their "
"foes!"
msgstr ""

#: .\Monsters\closeBandits.json
